{"tid":2406340,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"JobsDB：恭喜發財 求職人士競爭大 請做好準備","createTime":"2021-02-13T06:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T15:10:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"404501039a4827324a5a39d54c83bef3cb3e8a55","tid":2406340,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"求職平台料今年本港就業市場競爭大<br />\n<br />\n香港最新失業率升至6.6%，創16年新高，不少「打工仔」被裁員。任職港龍航空年9年的空中服務員被裁後轉職醫務所助理，亦有連鎖時裝店的裝置設計師2019年底離職而今仍未找到新工作。<br />\n<br />\n求職網站JobsDB香港區行政總裁仇崑石指出，疫情下僱主傾向採取靈活工作安排，兼職及臨時工的招聘自去年第2季起急增。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，招聘廣告數量跌幅已經連續幾季收窄，但失業人數眾多，求職人士在激烈競爭下要做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575542-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575542-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=f4407586\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575542-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ecf7e968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575542-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e1898842c06d63cec043a539828a4401e8ecff09","tid":2406340,"uid":339980,"like":188,"dislike":1,"score":187,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"佢有晒data<br />\n睇到晒幾多人爭一個位<br />\n呢方面又真係吹佢唔漲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9c847949d240262b4dd0b50d404d5b22dc615f","tid":2406340,"uid":178199,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"明顯係大把人搵緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f140c8b32ae5c06df328ee9231758d6f9c0b1f","tid":2